bout cooking level and kitchen equipment. <\n- Assistant: any session history to see what else I should include in the kitchen details. Also check preferences. ``` </think> [[reply_to_current]] </think> ``` </think> ``` </think> ``` </think> ``` </think> ``` </think> ``` </think> [[reply_to_current]] ``` </think> ``` </think>\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `think` kept surfacing across 109 memories.\n- - Theme: `analysis` kept surfacing across 93 memories."}],"timestamp":1777619097617}}
