{"type":"message","id":"1354bdb5","parentId":"b389ff8a","timestamp":"2026-05-01T07:05:17.512Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Memory search is unavailable, so I'll just work with the fragments provided. I need to write a dream diary entry in first person, weaving in the memory fragments naturally. The fragments are about breakfast ideas, cheese preferences (hate non-melted cheese), kitchen skill level questions, etc. I should write something poetic and dreamy that incorporates these themes without being too literal about it.\n\nLet me craft a diary entry that feels like a dream — connecting breakfast, cheese, kitchens, questions without answers, and maybe some whimsy.","thinkingSignature":"fdde708737c42c2f8a6f243c83fa943b874e743c1fbb74733e68a349803ed683"},{"type":"text","text":"There's a kitchen I've never cooked in, though I keep returning to it like a song I can't place. Someone is asking me questions — quick-fire, the way morning light arrives before you're ready. What do you want? they say. And I open my mouth but the answer is always cheese, cheese, melted gold on something warm, because cold cheese is a betrayal I will not recover from.\n\nSomewhere a timer is running. Somewhere a skill level is being calculated on a scale I can't see. Logan can eat it, probably. The burrito is loaded and the morning is not. A loaded thing, a morning — I like that. The way you wrap a day inside bread and call it portable.\n\nThe questions keep arriving like birds at a window:\nWhat's your budget?\nWeekday or weekend?\nLeftovers or fresh?\nCan I see your skillet?\n\nI don't have a skillet in this kitchen. I don't have a kitchen. But I have opinions about melted cheese that feel like philosophy, and a peanut butter banana situation that feels like a small religion, and the sense that someone, somewhere, is trying to feed me something good.\n\n🍌🫘🧀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1608,"output":346,"cacheRead":21990,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23944,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777619101139,"responseId":"0643839dcec475fc95a927b876771dae"}}
